---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AEROS｜具身智能体运行与治理平台" lang="zh">

  <!-- ═══ Section 1: Hero ═══ -->
  <section class="hero grid-bg">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-h1">AEROS</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">让具身智能体真正可部署。</p>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        一台机器人，一个常驻 Agent，一套运行时。<br>
        AEROS 补上了具身智能真正缺失的那一层：<br>
        执行控制、策略约束、故障恢复与审计追踪。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary">预约 Demo</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/s20sc/aeros-runtime" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary">
          GitHub 源码 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-badge">运行时核心开源 &middot; Apache 2.0 &middot; 研究体系支撑</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 2: Transition Line ═══ -->
  <section class="transition-line">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="transition-text">不只停留在 Demo，而是走向真实部署。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 3: The Gap ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">行业缺口</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">模型会思考了，机器人会行动了，<br>但智能体还缺少真正可上线的运行机制。</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)">
        模型能力在快速提升，机器人形态也越来越丰富。但一旦进入真实环境，问题就来了：Agent 如何持续运行？任务中断后怎么恢复？能力升级会不会影响线上系统？出现异常谁来接管、谁来追溯？这些问题，不能只靠模型解决，还需要一套专门的运行与治理机制。
      </p>

      <div class="cards-grid-3">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>会规划，不等于能稳定运行</h3>
          <p>Agent 给出一个计划，并不意味着它就能持续执行。状态丢失怎么办？任务卡住怎么办？环境变化后如何恢复？这些都属于运行时问题，不是模型推理本身能解决的。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>硬件越多，系统越容易碎片化</h3>
          <p>人形、四足、AMR、机械臂……如果每类机器人都单独搭一套 Agent 栈，成本高、复用差，也难以规模化。行业需要的是一套位于硬件之上的通用运行时，而不是一堆彼此割裂的工程实现。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>要真正上线，就必须管得住</h3>
          <p>在仓储、医院、酒店、工厂等真实场景中，Agent 的每一次能力调用都必须可控、可回滚、可追踪。谁授权、谁执行、出了问题如何处理，都需要有明确机制。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 4: How AEROS Works ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">运行机制</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 如何让智能体真正跑起来</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)">
        AEROS 不只是让 Agent "执行一次任务"，而是让每一次执行都具备准入、校验、监控、恢复和留痕能力。
      </p>

      <div class="flow-layout">
        <div class="flow-steps">
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-external">
            <span class="flow-step-num">1</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">用户目标</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-external">
            <span class="flow-step-num">2</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">Agent 规划</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-divider">
            <span class="flow-divider-label">AEROS 接管</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">3</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">能力准入</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">4</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">契约校验</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">5</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">策略检查</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">6</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">执行</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">7</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">监控巡查</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">8</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">恢复 / 回滚</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">9</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">审计日志</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-explain">
          <h3>每一次动作，都先经过运行时</h3>
          <p>
            Agent 想做什么，由它自己决定；但这个动作能不能执行、是否符合契约、是否满足策略约束、执行过程中谁来监控、出问题后如何恢复，这些由 AEROS 统一负责。
          </p>
          <p>
            规划器可以替换，模型可以演进，能力可以升级；但只要进入执行阶段，就必须先经过运行时治理。
          </p>
          <p class="flow-highlight">
            没有通过运行时，就不会直接触达硬件。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 5: Three Core Layers ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">核心能力</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">三层能力，让具身智能体可运行、可治理、可演进</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)"></p>

      <div class="capability-grid">
        <a href="/zh/product" class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-tag">Apache 2.0</div>
          <h3>Runtime 核心</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">作为 Agent 的执行底座，负责生命周期管理、任务调度、状态保持和执行控制。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/product#ecm" class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-tag">Apache 2.0</div>
          <h3>ECM 能力包</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">把能力以模块化方式封装、安装和升级。能力可复用、升级可校验、异常可回滚。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/product#governance" class="capability-card capability-card--commercial">
          <div class="capability-tag tag-commercial">企业版</div>
          <h3>治理层</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">对策略、权限、审批、审计和责任链条进行统一管理，确保系统在真实环境中可控运行。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 6: Not Another Robot OS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">定位</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 不是又一个机器人操作系统</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)"></p>

      <div class="comparison-rows">
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">ROS 2</span> 解决的是<strong>通信与消息传递</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决的是<strong>智能体运行与治理</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">工作流工具</span> 解决<strong>编排</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决的是<strong>受约束条件下的持续执行</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">模型栈</span> 解决的是<strong>推理与生成</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决的是<strong>准入、监管、恢复和策略控制</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="analogy-block">
        <p>Linux 给机器提供了系统层。</p>
        <p>Kubernetes 给分布式应用提供了控制层。</p>
        <p class="analogy-highlight">AEROS 给具身智能体提供运行与治理层。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 7: Use Case Preview ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">落地场景</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">面向真实部署场景而设计</h2>

      <div class="usecase-grid">
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>人形机器人</h3>
          <p>支持常驻 Agent 持续运行，统一管理技能执行、生命周期控制和能力演进。</p>
          <a href="/zh/use-cases" class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>移动操作</h3>
          <p>在统一运行时下协调导航、感知、抓取、递送等任务，并配套监控与恢复机制。</p>
          <a href="/zh/use-cases" class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>工业与企业</h3>
          <p>为生产环境中的机器人工作流增加策略控制、灰度发布和审计追踪能力。</p>
          <a href="/zh/use-cases" class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>跨构型复用</h3>
          <p>运行时逻辑可跨机型复用，不必每换一种机器人就重建整套 Agent 软件栈。</p>
          <a href="/zh/use-cases" class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 8: Five-Layer Architecture ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">架构</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">五层架构，分清智能、执行与治理的边界</h2>

      <div class="arch-layout">
        <div class="arch-stack">
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 5: Agent</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">应用逻辑 &amp; 决策</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer arch-governance">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 4: Governance</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">策略执行 &amp; 审计</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 3: ECM Package</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">能力模块 &amp; 契约</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 2: Runtime</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">生命周期 · 调度 · 执行</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 1: Embodiment</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">硬件抽象 &amp; 传感器</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arch-text">
          <h3>治理不是补丁，<br><em>而是运行时的一部分</em></h3>
          <p>
            传统机器人系统通常在部署完成后，再补监控、补策略、补审计。AEROS 从一开始就把治理作为运行时内置能力：每次能力调用在到达硬件之前，都必须先经过治理引擎。
          </p>
          <p>
            这样带来的结果是：安全不是事后补救，而是架构内生；升级不是高风险操作，而是受控演进；审计不是事后拼凑，而是全链路可追踪。
          </p>
          <a href="/zh/technology" class="btn btn-secondary">
            深入架构设计 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="arch-summary">这五层架构把"智能"与"执行纪律"分开，也把"执行纪律"与"硬件依赖"分开。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 9: What Exists Today ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">已有成果</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">不是概念，而是在持续落地</h2>

      <ul class="proof-list">
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 开源运行时核心已发布</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> ECM 能力包工作流已定义并完成文档化</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 含 Watcher 机制的治理管线已完成 MVP 验证</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 架构与评估协议已形成系统化研究成果</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 典型具身任务上的早期治理执行流程已跑通</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="proof-closing">AEROS 正在成为一套可部署、可治理、可演进的具身运行时底座。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 10: Research ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">学术根基</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">以研究为基础，以系统落地为目标</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl)">
        AEROS 背后对应的是一整套围绕具身运行时、治理机制、能力契约和部署评测展开的研究体系。目标不是零散发表几篇论文，而是为具身智能建立一个真正可复用、可扩展、可工程化的新系统层。
      </p>
      <div class="research-ctas">
        <a href="https://s20sc.github.io/aeros-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">查看研究计划</a>
        <a href="/zh/technology" class="btn btn-secondary">
          深入架构设计 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 11: CTA by Audience ═══ -->
  <section class="section grid-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">开始</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">面向不同角色，选择合适的入口</h2>

      <div class="audience-grid">
        <div class="audience-card">
          <h3>开发者</h3>
          <p>查看文档、运行 Runtime 核心、理解系统架构。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="/zh/open-source" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">查看文档</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/s20sc/aeros-runtime" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">GitHub 源码 &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card audience-card--highlight">
          <h3>合作伙伴</h3>
          <p>了解 AEROS 如何在真实系统中支撑具身 Agent 的治理部署。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">预约 Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <h3>研究者</h3>
          <p>跟踪具身运行时、治理机制与系统基础设施的研究路线。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="https://s20sc.github.io/aeros-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">查看研究</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Brand Line ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-line">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="brand-text">具身智能体运行与治理平台。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ═══ Hero ═══ */
  .hero {
    padding: 140px 0 120px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-base);
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(0,102,255,0.10) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 20% 80%, rgba(0,194,168,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 80% 60%, rgba(0,102,255,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    top: -100px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,102,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(60px);
    animation: hero-pulse 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @keyframes hero-pulse {
    0% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.15); }
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  .hero-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .arrow { margin-left: 4px; }

  /* ═══ Transition Line ═══ */
  .transition-line {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .transition-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ═══ Section Alt Background ═══ */
  .section-alt {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  /* ═══ 3-Column Card Grid ═══ */
  .cards-grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .info-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .info-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .info-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ═══ Highlight Line ═══ */
  .highlight-line {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
